   <p><b>How to use</b></p>
   
   <p>First things first, thank you for downloading this app! Some tips:</p>

<p>
&#8226; Now you can organize your todo items in categories ! change the current category by moving your finger left and right<br/>
&#8226; The keyboard opens at startup. You can change this behavior in the menu<br/>
&#8226; Add an item: input your text then select the priority<br/>
&#8226; Remove an item: Long press on it, or use the menu.<br/>
&#8226; Edit an item: long press (remove) it to copy the text on the input area, edit it and select the priority to add it as a new item<br/>
&#8226; You can use symbols instead of the color code (see the menu)<br/>
&#8226; You can change the font size from the menu<br/>  
</p>
	    
   
